data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to Nova Grove, where luxury meets comfort! This 5-bed, 3.5-bath home boasts a private fenced yard, heated pebble tech pool under a screened in lanai space and freshly laid sod. Step into this charming home featuring a spacious dining room perfect for hosting memorable gatherings.  The gourmet kitchen, equipped with quartz counters and stainless steel appliances, is a chef's dream offering a delightful space for culinary creations and casual dining.  The open floor plan, adorned with new flooring. The primary bedroom offers a spa-like retreat with dual shower heads and a garden tub located right across from the kitchen.  The Solar panels that help with your energy bill are paid off, low-E windows, and spray-foam insulation make it energy-efficient. Upstairs, a bonus room and office space add versatility with 4 other bedrooms and 2 full baths upstairs.  This community offers a lot of activities for the entire family.  Community potlucks, firepit nights, food truck gatherings and more.  Conveniently located near Lake Nona, Medical City, and major highways, this home is your gateway to luxury living!
